JLT Offers Specialist Cover to Pharmaceutical Companies, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-25T01:30:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/jlt-offers-specialist-cover-to-pharmaceutical-companies-ft-says.html
Jardine Lloyd Thompson Group Plc (JLT)  has
started offering “earnings and product integrity” insurance to
pharmaceutical companies seeking to shield themselves from the
risk of disruption and lost sales at plants closed by regulatory
inspections, from legal challenges to their patents and from
product recalls prompted by counterfeiting, the Financial Times
reported, citing the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 